<text id="02-output-contract" title="Hierarchical Runner Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schemas for the manager-emitted Plan, worker-emitted Result, and final Synthesis envelope.</summary>

  <section title="Plan schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/hierarchical-plan.v1.json",
  "title": "Plan",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["schema_version", "task", "assignments", "failure_policy"],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": {"type": "string", "const": "v1"},
    "task": {"type": "string", "minLength": 16},
    "failure_policy": {"type": "string", "enum": ["abort", "degrade", "retry"]},
    "assignments": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["id", "worker_name", "subtask", "deps", "timeout_s"],
        "properties": {
          "id": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^a[0-9]+$"},
          "worker_name": {"type": "string"},
          "subtask": {"type": "string", "minLength": 16},
          "deps": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}},
          "timeout_s": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 5}
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Result + Synthesis schemas">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "title": "WorkerResult",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["schema_version", "assignment_id", "worker_name", "status", "payload"],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": {"type": "string", "const": "v1"},
    "assignment_id": {"type": "string"},
    "worker_name": {"type": "string"},
    "status": {"type": "string", "enum": ["ok", "timeout", "error"]},
    "payload": {"type": ["object", "null"]},
    "error": {"type": ["string", "null"]}
  }
}

{
  "title": "Synthesis",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["schema_version", "task", "final_result", "used_tokens", "trace"],
  "properties": {
    "schema_version": {"type": "string", "const": "v1"},
    "task": {"type": "string"},
    "final_result": {"type": "object"},
    "used_tokens": {"type": "integer"},
    "trace": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object"}}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example (excerpt)">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{"schema_version":"v1","task":"Audit auth subsystem and produce a tightening plan","failure_policy":"degrade","assignments":[
  {"id":"a1","worker_name":"researcher","subtask":"List all auth-related code paths","deps":[],"timeout_s":60},
  {"id":"a2","worker_name":"security_reviewer","subtask":"Score each path against OWASP ASVS","deps":["a1"],"timeout_s":90},
  {"id":"a3","worker_name":"writer","subtask":"Draft the tightening plan markdown","deps":["a1","a2"],"timeout_s":90}]}
]]></code>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{"task":"x","assignments":[{"id":"a1","worker_name":"x","subtask":"do","deps":["a2"],"timeout_s":2},{"id":"a2","worker_name":"y","subtask":"do","deps":["a1"],"timeout_s":2}]}
]]></code>
      <note>Cycle a1↔a2 (rule r2), subtask too short, missing schema_version, missing failure_policy, timeouts &lt; minimum.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Plan parses as JSON; assignments[*].id form `a\d+`.</item>
      <item>DAG: deps[] contains only previously-defined ids; no cycle.</item>
      <item>Every worker named in assignments exists in the spec's roster.</item>
      <item>failure_policy is one of `abort | degrade | retry`.</item>
      <item>Every assignment has `timeout_s` ≥ 5.</item>
      <item>Synthesis carries `used_tokens` and full trace.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
